---
title: Chicken & Chargrilled Capsicum Mayo with Roast Veggie Coin Toss
description: Chicken is one of those dinner time dishes that demands attention. This one is golden, drizzled in a chargrillled capsicum mayo, and served atop a bed of roasted veggies. Every bite is a delightful surprise!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
